videos.headline: South Carolina wins national championship to complete perfect season
videos.description: South Carolina outlasts Iowa to win its third national championship and complete its 38-0 perfect season.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_OnePlay (South Carolina wins national championship to complete perfect season) 2024/4/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina outlasts Iowa to win its 3rd national title
videos.description: South Carolina defeats Iowa 87-75 to win its third national title under Dawn Staley.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (South Carolina outlasts Iowa to win its 3rd national title) 2024/4/7 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Kate Martin splashes the opening 3 for Iowa
videos.description: Kate Martin drills a catch-and-shoot 3-pointer to give Iowa an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kate Martin splashes the opening 3 for Iowa) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: 'Oh my!' Caitlin Clark drains a 3 from way downtown
videos.description: Caitlin Clark hits a deep 3-pointer as Iowa stays hot early vs. South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play ('Oh my!' Caitlin Clark drains a 3 from way downtown) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark hugs Iowa teammates as she's subbed out to end NCAA career
videos.description: Caitlin Clark hugs her teammates as she is subbed out in the final seconds of the women's NCAA championship game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark hugs Iowa teammates as she's subbed out to end NCAA career) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hannah Stuelke denies Kamilla Cardoso's layup attempt
videos.description: Hannah Stuelke meets Kamilla Cardoso at the top to deny the layup attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hannah Stuelke denies Kamilla Cardoso's layup attempt) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: MiLaysia Fulwiley knocks down a 3-pointer for South Carolina
videos.description: MiLaysia Fulwiley drains a 3-pointer as South Carolina reduces the deficit vs. Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (MiLaysia Fulwiley knocks down a 3-pointer for South Carolina) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark's 3-pointer sets NCAA women's basketball championship record
videos.description: Caitlin Clark nails the 3-pointer to tally 18 points in the quarter, the most in a women's NCAA basketball championship game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark's 3-pointer sets NCAA women's basketball championship record) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark finds space and makes an Iowa 3-pointer
videos.description: Caitlin Clark catches the ball on the wing and knocks down the 3-pointer for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark finds space and makes an Iowa 3-pointer) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kamilla Cardoso swats away the Iowa layup
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso makes easy work of this Iowa layup with a nice block.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kamilla Cardoso swats away the Iowa layup) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sydney Affolter drains the corner 3 for Iowa
videos.description: Sydney Affolter finds space in the corner and knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sydney Affolter drains the corner 3 for Iowa) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tessa Johnson ties things up with a South Carolina 3
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso kicks it to Tessa Johnson who knocks down the 3-pointer for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Tessa Johnson ties things up with a South Carolina 3) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark retakes the lead for Iowa with a step-back 3
videos.description: Caitlin Clark finds space with a step back and drains the 3-pointer for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark retakes the lead for Iowa with a step-back 3) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Raven Johnson strips Caitlin Clark and gets the layup for South Carolina
videos.description: Raven Johnson picks Caitlin Clark's pocket and makes the layup before the half for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Raven Johnson strips Caitlin Clark and gets the layup for South Carolina) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark finds Gabbie Marshall for a 3-pointer
videos.description: Caitlin Clark finds a wide-open Gabbie Marshall for an Iowa corner 3.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark finds Gabbie Marshall for a 3-pointer) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark dimes Hannah Stuelke for an Iowa layup
videos.description: Caitlin Clark zips a pass to Hannah Stuelke for an Iowa layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark dimes Hannah Stuelke for an Iowa layup) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina's bench loves this Bree Hall 3
videos.description: Bree Hall knocks down a 3-pointer and the South Carolina bench loves it.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (South Carolina's bench loves this Bree Hall 3) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sydney Affolter muscles in the and-1 for Iowa
videos.description: Sydney Affolter drives to the rim and finishes the layup plus the foul for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sydney Affolter muscles in the and-1 for Iowa) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kamilla Cardoso comes up with a huge swat for South Carolina
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso protects the rim with a big-time block for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kamilla Cardoso comes up with a huge swat for South Carolina) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kamilla Cardoso grabs the offensive board and makes the layup
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso corrals the offensive rebound and gets a clutch putback layup for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kamilla Cardoso grabs the offensive board and makes the layup) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dawn Staley emotional after South Carolina wins national championship
videos.description: Dawn Staley can't hold back her emotions in an interview after winning the women's NCAA championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Dawn Staley emotional after South Carolina wins national championship) 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark scores 30 points in final collegiate game
videos.description: Caitlin Clark scores 30 points in the national championship game, but it's not enough as Iowa falls to undefeated South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Caitlin Clark scores 30 points in final collegiate game) 2024/04/07 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Dawn Staley calls Caitlin Clark 'one of the GOATs of our game'
videos.description: South Carolina coach Dawn Staley heaps praise on Iowa star Caitlin Clark after her collegiate career comes to an end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Dawn Staley calls Caitlin Clark 'one of the GOATs of our game') 2024/04/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paopao, Johnson on South Carolina's crown, culture and more
videos.description: After winning the Gamecocks' third national title, Te-Hina Paopao and Tessa Johnson explain how their teammates give them the courage to play their best and reflect on their families' support.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (SC PaoPao Johnson) 240407

videos.headline: Feagin details South Carolina's journey, shouts out Johnson
videos.description: While celebrating the second national title of her career, Sania Feagin details the Gamecocks' journey from the summer to cutting down the nets and shouts out freshman Tessa Johnson.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (SC Sania) 240407

videos.headline: South Carolina's Staley gives Iowa, Clark their flowers
videos.description: Dawn Staley commends the Hawkeyes on an incredible season and shares her appreciation for Caitlin Clark, calling her "one of the GOATs of our game."

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (SC Staley on Clark) 240407

videos.headline: What strengths can Iowa and South Carolina use in the title game?
videos.description: Andraya Carter breaks down Iowa and South Carolina's strengths ahead of the women's NCAA championship game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Analysis (What strengths can Iowa and South Carolina use in the title game?) 2024/4/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gamecocks' 2024 title: Perfection with a touch of sweet redemption
videos.description: Dawn Staley converts her biggest challenge of the transition to a young roster into the rich reward of a national title fueled by South Carolina's depth, trust and talent.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Feature (SC redemption championship) 240407

videos.headline: How Dawn Staley built a South Carolina dynasty
videos.description: Elle Duncan details South Carolina's dominance under coach Dawn Staley and how the Gamecocks went undefeated to capture the women's NCAA title without returning any starters.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Feature (How Dawn Staley built a South Carolina dynasty) 2024/4/8 SCEU

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark: It's sad that this is all over
videos.description: Caitlin Clark looks back on Iowa's national championship run following its 87-75 loss to South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Presser (Caitlin Clark: It's sad that this is all over) 2024/4/7
